Class OI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.team1285.frc2016.OI

  • public class OI
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the glue that binds the controls on the physical operator interface to the commands and command groups that allow control of the robot. Used with the Logitech F310.
    Author:
    Kaveesha Siribaddana
